ades]] || {{cr|FIJ}} || [[Alan Apted]] || [[Bromsgrove Cricket Club Ground]], [[Bromsgrove]] || {{cr|BER}} by 51 runs\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331461/kenya-vs-united-states-of-america-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41a] || 21 June || {{cr|KEN}} || [[Ramesh Patel]] || {{cr|USA}} || [[Kamran Rasheed]] || [[Lichfield Cricket Club Ground]], [[Lichfield]] || Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331224/netherlands-vs-singapore-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41b] || 21 June || {{cr|NED}} || [[Dik Abed]] || {{cr|SIN}} || [[Stacey Muruthi]] || [[Fordhouses Cricket Club Ground]], [[Wolverhampton]] || {Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331154/bangladesh-vs-singapore-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41c] || 23 June || {{cr|BAN}} || [[Shafiq-ul-Haq]] || {{cr|SIN}} || [[Stacey Muruthi]] || [[Lutterworth Cricket Club Ground]], [[Lutterworth]] || Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331242/canada-vs-gibraltar-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41d] || 23 June || {{cr|CAN}} || [[Richard Stevens]] || {{cr|Gibraltar}} || [[Willie Scott (cricketer)|Willie Scott]] || [[Nuneaton Cricket Club Ground]], [[Nuneaton]] || Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331205/east-africa-vs-malaysia-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41e] || 23 June || {{cr|East Africa}} || [[Keith Arnold (cricketer)|Keith Arnold]] || {{cr|Malaysia}} || [[Zainon Mat]] || [[High Town Cricket Ground]], [[Bridgnorth]] || Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/331215/fiji-vs-west-africa-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 41f] || 23 June || {{cr|FIJ}} || [[Alan Apted]] || [[West Africa cricket team|West Africa]] || [[Ewa Henshaw]] || [[Barnt Green Cricket Club Ground]], [[Barnt Green]] || Match abandoned\n|-\n| [https://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8038/scorecard/66486/israel-vs-kenya-icc-trophy-1982 ICCT 42] || 23 June || {{cr|Israel}} || [[Hillel Awasker]] || {{cr|KEN}} || [[