rv |url=https://archive.org/details/battleofbritainm00over }} (hardcover, {{ISBN|0-393-32297-1}} paperback, 2002)\n* {{cite book |last=Overy |first=Richard J. |title=The Bombing War : Europe 1939\u20131945 |publisher=Allen Lane |location=London & New York |year=2013 |isbn=978-0-7139-9561-9 |ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last1=Pataky|first1=Iv\u00e1n|last2=Rozsos|first2=L\u00e1szl\u00f3|last3=S\u00e1rhidai|first3=Gyula|title=L\u00e9gi h\u00e1bor\u00fa Magyarorsz\u00e1g felett|trans-title=Air War over Hungary|date=1993|publisher=Zr\u00ednyi Kiad\u00f3|location=Budapest|isbn=963-327-173-8|volume=2|language=Hungarian|ref=harv}}\n* Poeppel, Hans and Prinz von Preu\u00dfen, Wilhelm-Karl and von Hase, Karl-G\u00fcnther. (2000) ''Die Soldaten der Wehrmacht.'' Herbig Verlag. {{ISBN|978-3-7766-2057-3}}\n* Price, Alfred. Kampfflieger -Bombers of the Luftwaffe January 1942-Summer 1943, Volume 3. 2005, Classic Publications. {{ISBN|978-1-903223-49-9}}\n* {{cite book |title=Fire and Fury: The Allied Bombing of Germany, 1942\u20131945 |last=Hansen |first=Randall |isbn=978-0-385-66403-5 |publisher=[[Doubleday Canada]] |year=2008 |location=Toronto |url=https://archive.org/details/firefuryalliedbo0000hans_k7d6 }}\n* {{cite book |author=RAF staff |date=6 April 2005 |url=http://www.raf.mod.uk/bombercommand/diary.html |title=Bomber Command Campaign Diary |work=Royal Air Force Bomber Command 60th Anniversary |ref=harv |archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20070706011932/http://www.raf.mod.uk/bombercommand/diary.html |archivedate=6 July 2007}}\n* Ray, John. ''The Night Blitz''. Booksales. {{ISBN|978-0-7858-1601-0}}.\n* {{cite book |last=Richards |first=Denis |work=Royal Air Force 1939\u20131945 |volume=I |title=The Fight at Odds |url=http://ftp.ibiblio.org/hyperwar/UN/UK/UK-RAF-I/index.html |year=1953 |publisher=Her Majesty's Stationery Office |location=London |access-date=13 February 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070904181633/http://ftp.ibiblio.org/hyperwar/U